PARTITION BY (str2date(`dt`, '%Y%m%d'))
DISTRIBUTED BY RANDOM

PROPERTIES (
"replicated_storage" = "true",

)
AS SELECT `f`.`dt` AS `dt1`, bitmap_union(to_bitmap(`f`.`becif_no`)) AS `count_distinct_serialno`, `f`.`dt`, `dim2`.`strategy_id_pdl` AS `dim2_strategy_id_pdl`, `f`.`data_date` AS `f_data_date`, `dim2`.`task_indicator_code` AS `dim2_task_indicator_code`, `dim3`.`node_code` AS `dim3_node_code`, `dim2`.`item_index_pdl` AS `dim2_item_index_pdl`, `dim3`.`travel_code` AS `dim3_travel_code`, `f`.`scene_id` AS `f_scene_id`, `dim2`.`cust_group_name` AS `dim2_cust_group_name`, `dim2`.`team_indicator_code` AS `dim2_team_indicator_code`, `f`.`event_type` AS `f_event_type`, `dim2`.`strategy_type` AS `dim2_strategy_type`
FROM `hive`.`test_db`.`tbl_d` AS `f` LEFT OUTER JOIN `hive`.`test_db`.`tbl_b` AS `dim3` ON (`f`.`trace_id` = `dim3`.`trace_id`) AND (`f`.`dt` = `dim3`.`dt`) LEFT OUTER JOIN `hive`.`test_db`.`tbl_e` AS `dim2` ON (`f`.`strategy_id_pdl` = `dim2`.`strategy_id_pdl`) AND (`f`.`dt` = `dim2`.`dt`)
